title: PACKET LOSS OVER TIME
body: looked at my logs for games and it tells me I have ALOT PACKET LOSS OVER Time ok? How do I fix that? I noticed when i play i click and commands don't go through it really annoying and started not to long after the last update. Here's my ping test if this helps [https://i.gyazo.com/8b0b8bf4eaa172e35eee146b0a0d655f.png](https://gyazo.com/8b0b8bf4eaa172e35eee146b0a0d655f)

replies.body: Let's go ahead and double check that packet loss with our [**log reader**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209765743), just because I'm not actually able to see any evidence of packet loss from that image you linked. Take a screenshot of what it says and post it here so that we can know for sure if this is packet loss we're dealing with.
